race.description: Carlton Draught Ollie Cox Memorial Handicap (Bm66)
race.comment: SAXON BEAUTY (7) ran a better race last start to finish a close second over 2050m at Moe after missing the placings at the previous appearance. Best efforts measure up so capable of another big run. EXPEETEE (1) was out of the money two runs back then again missed the frame last start over 1700m at Flemington, beaten 4.5 lengths into seventh. Brittany Button gets the best out of this five-year-old mare. Has the ability to put the recent run of form behind her. GARNACHO (4) was out of the money two runs back then again missed the frame last start over 2050m at Moe, beaten 1.5 lengths into fourth. Finds a suitable assignment and can get the job done.  BURLINGTON GATE (8) has been out of the placings in two runs since a break, the latest when eighth, beaten 5 lengths, over 1856m at Kyneton. AZEOLA (10) was out of the placings for the first time in a while last start, but wasn't beaten far and can play a role again.
